  At trigger 'ONCONNECT_2' line: 5, col: 29
ID          MSG
----------- ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1           Connect T1 as NONE
2           Connect T2 as NONE
3           Connect T3 as NONE
"""
}
